params.prompt:
Create a comprehensive table showing all 10 processing steps as a JSON array. For each step, provide: step name, the generated content (limit to 200 chars), and approximate word count. Return ONLY valid JSON array with NO markdown code blocks or formatting.

Step 1 - Initial Overview: {{step1_initial_content.text}}
Step 2 - Creative Version: {{step2_creative_variation}}
Step 3 - Professional Summary: {{step3_professional_summary}}
Step 4 - Structured Data: {{step4_structured_data.text}}
Step 5 - Marketing Copy: {{step5_marketing_copy.text}}
Step 6 - Technical Analysis: {{step6_technical_analysis}}
Step 7 - Social Media Posts: {{step7_social_media_version}}
Step 8 - FAQs: {{step8_faqs.text}}
Step 9 - Keywords & Tags: {{step9_keywords_tags}}

Format: [{"step": "...", "content": "...", "wordCount": "..."}]
